t24:fields.t24:gen-operation: IF COMM.TYPE THEN IF SUBR("ENQ.TRANS", "FD.COMM.CHANGE", COMM.TYPE, 0) THEN "1" ELSE "" ELSE ""

t24:fields.name: RENEWAL_RPT_REQ
t24:fields.t24:gen-operation: SUBR("ENQ.TRANS","FD.PARAMETER","SYSTEM",29) ; SUBR("E.CDT",CURRENCY[1,2],"","-":@1) ; SUBR("E.CDT",CURRENCY[1,2],"","+":@1) ; IF MATURITY.DATE GE @2 AND MATURITY.DATE LE @3 THEN "Y" ELSE "N"

t24:fields.name: OPEN_NOTICE_ORDER
t24:fields.t24:gen-operation: SUBR("ENQ.TRANS","FD.POOL.GROUP",POOLED.GROUP, "ORDER.STATUS") ; IF INDEX(@1,'OPEN',1) AND GROUP.STATUS = 'EXIST' THEN 1 ELSE IF GROUP.STATUS NE 'CLOSED' AND GROUP.STATUS NE 'EXIST' THEN 1 ELSE 0
